  "description": "Figure-eight at maximum tangle (0.9) — the self-intersection point of the ∞ shape becomes a collision zone. Energy fed through one loop immediately emerges from the crossing point and feeds the other loop. S&H randomly redirects the delay base for temporal chaos. This is what a signal looks like when it collides with itself.",
